<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Pi̱ki ʋba Chihowa ma!
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klo pulla cha,
 Chim anumpa holitopa
 Auet ish pima pullashke.

[V2]
 Pi okcha̱ya ta̱kla hoka
 Ish pi apela pulla na,
 Nitak moma himak pilla
 E chithaiyana pullashke.

[V3]
 Pi okcha̱ya taiyakla ka
 Ish pi apela pulla na,
 Nana isht ilaiyukpa ma
 Il ithaiyana pullashke.

[V4]
 Pi yʋmohmi pulla tuk osh
 Yakni ilʋppa ahantʋt,
 Pim ai ʋhli hokmak heno,
 Ish pi halʋlli pullashke.

[V5]
 Yʋmma il ona hokmʋto,
 Pi okcha̱ya bilia he,
 Il aiahni fehna kak osh,
 E chi aiokpahanchishke.</lyrics>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Pi̱ki ʋba Chihowa ma ƲIT83</title>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<hymn_number>83</hymn_number>
</song>